      "message": "I think it might be worth it to discuss the trade-offs of using SkScalarNearlyEqual.\n\nIMO this opens us up to rendering bugs when the view matrix is extreme. And I feel like it\u0027s pretty reasonable to expect that if somebody wants a circle, they will give us something with x\u003d\u003d\u003dy in the raw, untransformed radii.\n\nI might be inclined. Just check if \"x\u003d\u003dy\"? What do you think?",
